Still there using version 1.6.11.
Is there any way to have more details (verbose log or something)?
You can load PDB symbols (can be downloaded in Releases page) in the debugger to get a detailed stack trace, otherwise debugger would just show a symbol with close address.

I already did it. With the 1.6.11 the stack trace is the following.
Still have no clue on how creating a trace that can give a hint on what's happening here.

FYI, I repeated 1Million loop tests of the addin under node from console with no issues. I can't exclude a bug of mine, but I can observe it only under electron and I would like more info to understand the issue.
